node.title: Fog cancels flights in and out of Wellington Airport
node.description: Fog at Wellington Airport continues to force the cancellation of flights in and out of the capital.
node.content:
["Fog at Wellington Airport continues to force the cancellation of flights in and out of the capital.", "", "
Note: The information about the flights mentioned in this image may have changed, please check with the airline if you are booked on any flights in and out of Wellington Airport. Photo: Screengrab / Wellington Airport
", "Wellington International Airport said very few flights had been able to land in the past 24 hours.", "Many flights have been cancelled or diverted, mainly to Palmerston North.", "Many departures are also being cancelled or delayed.", "Passengers should expect cancellations and delays to continue even after the fog lifts, as airlines work to clear the backlog.", "MetService said the fog would lift briefly this afternoon before settling back over the airport until tomorrow afternoon."]
